OL,3,CThousands of homes without water and
OL,4,Cschools closed due to burst water main
OL,6,FThousands of people are without water
OL,7,Fin the Conwy Valley after a burst
OL,8,Fwater main at a treatment works near
OL,9,FDolgarrog.
OL,11,FWelsh Water have confirmed around
OL,12,F8,000 households have currently lost
OL,13,Fsupply, with a further 33,000 at risk
OL,14,Funtil the repair is completed.
OL,16,FThe burst main is at the Bryn Cowlyd
OL,17,FWater Treatment Works and is impacting
OL,18,Fproperties in Conwy, Colwyn Bay,
OL,19,FLlanrwst, Llandudno, Dolgarrog and
OL,20,Fsurrounding areas.
