OL,3,CThousands of homes without water and
OL,4,Cschools closed due to burst water main
OL,6,FDwr Cymru Welsh Water say they
OL,7,Fanticipate supplies will not be
OL,8,Frestored until later today, Thursday,
OL,9,F16 January, and bottled water is being
OL,10,Fdelivered to particularly vulnerable
OL,11,Fpeople, which equates to around 5,000
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,FThey say that they are tankering water
OL,15,Finto the network to maintain supplies
OL,16,Fto local hospitals. Six schools in
OL,17,FConwy have closed as a result of the
OL,18,Fburst main, with businesses impacted
OL,19,Falso closed.
