OL,3,CThousands of homes without water and
OL,4,Cschools closed due to burst water main
OL,6,FThe water company say that repairs are
OL,7,Fcurrently underway but the emergency
OL,8,Frepair is "difficult and dangerous"
OL,9,Fdue to the burst main being located
OL,10,Ftwo and a half meters under the river
OL,11,Fbed of Afon Ddu.
OL,13,FA dam like structure will be created
OL,14,Fin the river to allow specialist crews
OL,15,Fto access the damaged water main.
OL,17,FAccording to the Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,18,FWater, supply checker it is currently
OL,19,Fanticipated that supplies will be
OL,20,Frestored by 12pm.
