OL,3,CThousands of homes without water and
OL,4,Cschools closed due to burst water main
OL,6,FA Dwr Cymru Welsh Water spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are still dealing with a
OL,8,Fburst water main at our Bryn Cowlyd
OL,9,FWater Treatment Works, Dolgarrog,
OL,10,Fwhich is impacting water supplies to
OL,11,Fproperties across the Conwy Valley.
OL,13,F"Around 8,000 households lost supplies
OL,14,Flast night and around a further 33,000
OL,15,Fproperties are now at risk of losing
OL,16,Fsupplies until the repair is complete.
