OL,3,CThousands of homes without water and
OL,4,Cschools closed due to burst water main
OL,6,F"Our crews have been working on site
OL,7,Fovernight but this emergency repair is
OL,8,Fdifficult and dangerous as the burst
OL,9,Fwater main is two and half metres
OL,10,Fbeneath the local river bed (Afon
OL,11,FDdu)."
OL,13,FThe company said that the work
OL,14,Frequires specialist equipment and
OL,15,Finvolves having to create a dam-like
OL,16,Fstructure in the river to excavate and
OL,17,Faccess the damaged water main, whilst
OL,18,Fprotecting our workforce and the
OL,19,Fenvironment.
