OL,3,CThousands of homes without water and
OL,4,Cschools closed due to burst water main
OL,6,F"We will continue to keep customers
OL,7,Finformed today," the company said. "We
OL,8,Fapologise to anyone whose water supply
OL,9,Fis interrupted and would like to
OL,10,Freassure them we are working hard to
OL,11,Fresolve this significant incident.
OL,12,FCustomers can get the latest
OL,13,Finformation on our website:
OL,14,Fdwrcymru.com, on our social media
OL,15,Fchannels or by checking In Your Area
OL,16,Ffor updates."
